{"id": 3538, "title": "Ticket #3538: Support mixed IPv4/IPv6 mode", "description": "<blockquote>\nReplaced by Ticket <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4492\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4492'); return false;\" title=\"IPv6: General tracking ticket\">#4492</a></span>: IPv6: General tracking ticket\n\n<p>Condor should support mixed-mode IPv4/IPv6, so that on a host with both IPv4 and IPv6 connectivity, Condor should be able to use both, potentially simultaneously.\n\n</p><p>Current state: public review of design document.\n\n</p><p>Interested people in the design: Todd Tannenbaum, Brian Bockelman, Dale Carder, Francesco Prelz (willing to help with development)\n\n</p><p>Design document is at <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/a/wisc.edu/document/d/1BgKK9aHWPJGiePl4Kcv-cl1bbm8MPShG5d8gUf38N_s/edit#\">https://docs.google.com/a/wisc.edu/document/d/1BgKK9aHWPJGiePl4Kcv-cl1bbm8MPShG5d8gUf38N_s/edit#</a>\n\n</p><p>(Old design document, just in case: <span class=\"wiki\"><a href=\"wiki?p=DesignDocMixedModeFourSix\" title=\"Design Doc Mixed Mode Four Six\">DesignDocMixedModeFourSix</a></span>.)\n\n</p><p></p><div>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" summary=\"EMBED: Status Table of Derived Tickets\">\n<caption>\n  <a href=\"rptview?rn=86\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"EMBED: Status Table of Derived Tickets\">EMBED: Status Table of Derived Tickets</a>\n</caption>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td colspan=\"11\"><form action=\"rptview\" method=\"GET\">\n<input name=\"rn\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"86\"/>\nTN: <input name=\"TN\" type=\"text\" value=\"3538\"/>\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Go\"/>\n</form></td></tr> \n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"rptview?rn=86&amp;order_by=2&amp;order_dir=ASC&amp;TN=3538\">Developer</a></th>\n<th><a href=\"rptview?rn=86&amp;order_by=3&amp;order_dir=ASC&amp;TN=3538\">#</a></th>\n<th><a href=\"rptview?rn=86&amp;order_by=4&amp;order_dir=ASC&amp;TN=3538\">Status</a></th>\n<th><a href=