<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://hepix-ipv6.web.cern.ch/\">Group testing IPv6 support for LHC computing grid applications.</a> <a class=\"external\" href=\"http://hepix-ipv6.web.cern.ch/wlcg-applications\">Index of software they're testing.</a> <a class=\"external\" href=\"http://hepix-ipv6.web.cern.ch/content/condor\">HTCondor-specific information.</a>\n\n</p><p></p><hr/>\n<em>2015-Jun-03 14:09:30 by tlmiller:</em> <br/>\n\nTimT, the commits on this ticket don't need documentation.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"abandoned\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3853\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3853'); return false;\" title=\"Extend Sinful for mixed IPv4/IPv6 mode\">#3853</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nExtend Sinful for mixed IPv4/IPv6 mode</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-May-06 11:13</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/b077a09fe63caf1bc729d1a2670d745e1b4c13b1\">[44795]</a></span>: Squashed commit of the following: commit 138b863503f2a5bda1777cf5f6a352c48d7db3a2 Author: Todd L Miller &lt;tlmiller@cs.wisc.edu&gt; Date: Tue May 5 15:03:24 2015 -0500\u00a0[...]\n (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Apr-23 15:09</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \n